tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE car_models (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(50),
    engine_size DECIMAL(4,2),
    horsepower INT,
    length DECIMAL(5,2),
    width DECIMAL(5,2),
    height DECIMAL(5,2)
);

CREATE TABLE car_models (
    model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(50),
    engine_type VARCHAR(50),
    engine_size FLOAT,
    horsepower INT
);

CREATE TABLE engine_specifications (
    engine_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT REFERENCES car_models(model_id),
    cylinder_count INT,
    max_torque FLOAT,
    fuel_type VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE car_dimensions (
    dimension_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id INT REFERENCES car_models(model_id),
    length FLOAT,
    width FLOAT,
    height FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE CarModels (
  model_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  model_name VARCHAR(255),
  engine_type VARCHAR(50),
  engine_displacement FLOAT,
  horsepower INT,
  torque INT
);

CREATE TABLE EngineSpecifications (
  engine_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  engine_type VARCHAR(50),
  manufacturer VARCHAR(100),
  cylinders INT,
  displacement FLOAT,
  max_power INT,
  max_torque INT
);

CREATE TABLE Dimensions (
  dimension_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  length FLOAT,
  width FLOAT,
  height FLOAT,
  weight FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE car_models(
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name STRING,
    engine_type STRING,
    engine_displacement FLOAT,
    horsepower INT,
    torque FLOAT,
    year INT
);

CREATE TABLE engine_specifications(
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    engine_type STRING,
    cylinders INT,
    displacement FLOAT,
    fuel_type STRING,
    compression_ratio FLOAT,
    hp_per_liter FLOAT
);

CREATE TABLE dimensions(
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id UUID,
    length FLOAT,
    width FLOAT,
    height FLOAT,
    weight FLOAT
);
